Subject: Using meta tag "description" in html pages

Hi!
I have a problem with lucene. When it searches something the results are
compossed by 2 fields, title and description.
The description seems to be the beginning of the page, and due to the fact
that all my pages have the same beginning y need to personalize this.
Some other engines use meta tags to do this, a "description" meta tag. I
think that it's not supported now by lucene, but it's expected to be
supported in the next version.
When is the next version (1.3) expected to be out?

