Hi friens,
I had now created index with the org.apache.lucene.demo.IndexHTML .
the syntax i had given is "java org.apache.lucene.demo.IndexHTML -create -index d:\index %catalina_home%/webapps/textdocs"

It had created the index . I had used this index in configuration.jsp. and the Search is producing result . But the url returned by the search in for local document in the form of d:\tomcat\tomcat-jakarta\webapps\textdocs\xyz.htm

But i want url of my documents in the form of http://mywebsite:8080/textdocs/xyz.htm

How can i achieve this . Please help me in this matter.

Regards
Ravi



