and indexed but not tokenized. The value of the field is "POST"=20
(uppercase). But the only way i can match the field is by entering=20
"element:POST?" or "element:POST*" in the QueryParser class.

Have anyone here run into this problem?

I am using the 1.2 release version of Lucene.

Mvh Karl =D8ie


